  m_text: 'STANDARD PROCEDURE



    Welcome to the scene, detective. Your job is
    simple. Explore the town, talk to the locals, and gather evidence.



    Once
    you have enough pieces of the puzzle, head back to the trunk of your ''89 Civic.
    Connect the evidence, find the motive, and catch the killer.'
